Brace Sproul

 Report this post

Agent Builder is out now! Go from an idea to a fully functional agent in under a minute just by describing what you want!

LangChain

472,955 followers

LangSmith Agent Builder is our no code agent builder for anyone to create an agent, now available in private preview. This is not a workflow builder. Built on our Deep Agents architecture, LangSmith Agent Builder handles planning, memory, and sub-agents automatically. This means you can get your agent working faster without planning out every edge case. This is our first foray into allowing business users to build agents. OPEN DEEP RESEARCH!!! We're extremely excited to release our open source deep research agent! This agent excels at high quality research and report generation over not only web searches, but also internal data sources!! Along with the repo, we've also released a blog post diving into the architecture, design decisions, and lessons we learned while building it. Check out the repo, blog, YouTube video, and demo on Open Agent Platform today: OSS Repo:  Blog:  Video:  Open Agent Platform demo:
